name: Buddy
description: Friendly and energetic golden retriever who loves to play fetch. Great with kids and other dogs.
trainer_notes: Buddy responds well to positive reinforcement. Focus on leash manners and impulse control during walks.

name: Luna
description: Smart and loyal companion. Very food motivated and loves training.
trainer_notes: Luna is reactive to other dogs on leash. Use BAT 2.0 protocol. Keep 15ft distance from triggers.

name: Charlie
description: Sweet beagle with a curious nose. Calm and affectionate family dog.

name: Max
description: High-energy chocolate lab who loves water and fetching.

name: Daisy
description: Incredibly intelligent and eager to please. Excels at agility.

name: Cooper
description: Beautiful blue merle coat. Energetic and smart.

name: Bella
description: Gorgeous husky with striking blue eyes. Loves cool weather and long runs.

name: Zeus
description: Gentle giant who thinks he's a lap dog. Calm and affectionate.

name: Rosie
description: Adorable corgi mix with short legs and big personality!
